Products.FullDescription: Bill's Health Bakery Multifruit Sourdough Loaf
Products.RichDescription:
Bill's Organic Sourdough Multi Fruit is a great source of antioxidants.

Bill's certified organic stoneground multifruit sourdough is simply unique. Packed with antioxidant goodness from certified organic sultanas, raisins, figs and apricots, all naturally preserved without sulphites. Sulphites can affect some asthmatics and can be the cause of allergies and sensitivities. A delicious combination of sourdough and fruit - but best of all tastes amazing!

At Bill's, we're focused on inspiring healthier living through healthier choices. All of our delicious sourdoughs are made using pure, natural ingredients from certified organic farms, milling our flour in a traditional stoneguard method, and allowing our unique natural starter to slowly ferment over 18 hours. Simple. Certified Organic and no nasties.

Why 'Certified' Organic? Because we believe it is absolutely essential when creating our highly nutritious and tasty sourdoughs. When you purchase certified organic produce you can be guaranteed (through strict external regular auditing by Australian Certified Organic from farm to plate) that what you're eating is free from harmful artificial fertilisers and chemicals as well as promoting ethical farming practices.

High in fibre.

Vegan & No dairy.

Lower GI & pH.

Non-GMO.

Low fat.

Cholesterol free.

Nut free.

Reduced salt.

Free from:

- Artificial preservatives.

- Flavourings and colouring.

No added soy.

No added yeast.

No added sugar.

No animal products.

No chemical herbicides & pesticides.

Healthy living never tasted better.

Naturally preserved.

Certified organic fruits.

Products.RichDescription:
Spelt is an ancinet grain - a highly nutritious alternative to conventional wheat. A safe substitute for those who experience sensitivities to conventional wheat Spelt is easily soluble in water allowing nutrients to be efficiently absorbed by our bodies, making to easy to digest. High in protein (significantly higher than conventional wheat) and B complex vitamins spelt is packed full of simple and complex carbohydrates. These are both important for blood clotting and stimulating the body's immune system. Spelt is a superb fibre resource. You'll love spelt not just because its nutty flavour tastes so good but because it is bursting with so many other nutritional benefits which are amazingly good for you!

At Bill's, we're focused on inspiring healthier living through healthier choices. All of our delicious sourdoughs are made using pure, natural ingredients from certified farms, milling our flour in a traditional stoneground method, and allowing our unique natural starter to slowly ferment over 18 hours. Simple, certified Organic and no nasties.

- High in fibre.

- Vegan & no dairy.

- Lower GI & pH.

- Non GMO.

- Low fat.

- Cholesterol free.

- Nut free.

- Reduced salt.

Free from

- Artificial preservatives.

- Flavourings and colouring.

- No added soy.

- No added yeast.

- No added sugar.

- No animal products.

- No chemical herbicides & pesticides.

Olive Sourdough Loaf

Proudly made with Australian wheat flour, these sourdough bread recipes have been crafted by an expert artisan baker. Using time honoured methods, the 40 hour recipe loaves begin with a traditional culture, are slowly fermented then hand shaped and rested before being fully baked on stone. Finished in our in-store ovens, these loaves have an intense sourdough flavour, with a perfect crust and wonderful open texture. Find out more Here

- No Added Yeast
- Naturally Leavened 
- Hand Shaped
